{"tid":942031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"天降橫財：途人執到「成舊水」　轉頭遭警員沒收","createTime":"2018-12-15T10:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T19:16:51.000Z","uid":66271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"42acf729300f78e5a31dfe72d2ef596c41c80e97","tid":942031,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:22:43.000Z","msg":"深水埗今午(15日)有人從大廈天台撒下大疊鈔票，引來大批途人哄搶「執錢」。其中一名成功執到一張100港元紙幣的女途人，表示「真係好彩，唔知點用，可能一陣去買嘢！」惟有女士坦言不知道此舉是否犯法，坦言「咁啱經過執到」。<br />\n<br />\n適時，2名警員見狀上前了解，要求登記該名女子個人資料，並將其執到的紙幣沒收。對於橫財瞬間「得而復失」，女途人無奈地表示：「有少少後悔呀！」<br />\n<br />\n另一名拾到300元的外籍女傭亦表現興奮，指將會在聖誕假期時留港消費。拾到100元的葉婆婆事後同樣笑至合不攏嘴，她表示將用天降的橫財「買啲靚衫着。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsGxBoD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsGxBoD.png&h=4273b9c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jGmBiB0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjGmBiB0.png&h=d6b5e409&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRyW23G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRyW23G.png&h=640028ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSeGuJH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSeGuJH.png&h=0525bc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef3c74b0eb80c52cd4793f83f868fc2b7d22caa8","tid":942031,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:23:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a313c3c3511ce6b930355d8470db6f04b58773","tid":942031,"uid":192409,"like":15,"dislike":4,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"無偷無搶 犯條撚法咩"},{"pid":"e5eefe4295587e08f0b2a0f88e2d20b1767822a0","tid":942031,"uid":67346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:25:34.000Z","msg":"憑邊條法例沒收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5304ce99246294c0552d7f28980d8a87064baa","tid":942031,"uid":173159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:27:30.000Z","msg":"過幾個月冇人認投就會打電話俾你攞翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef23f886d3a3b142538a6e149703172fba200e3","tid":942031,"uid":67876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"律師梁永鏗接受訪問時表示，市民在街上執到屬於他人擁有及具有價值的財物，例如現金等，沒有將財物交予警方反而擅自據為己有，其行為等同拾遺不報，有可能已觸犯盜竊罪，一旦罪名成立，最高刑期是判監10年。「因為呢啲財物根本就唔係屬於佢哋（執拾者）。財物擁有人如果表明唔要或者將財物丟去垃圾站，咁嘅情況去執就唔算有罪，未必觸犯到法律」。<br />\n好似佢話拍片從天而降<br />\n又無講明派街坊 都要俾翻警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7785d6a2efaa7b6b64f3717223a7d1028ca28ad4","tid":942031,"uid":177039,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"呀蛇袋袋平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f320affd42179b1ebcf10065e47a25e2ab1439","tid":942031,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ef23f886d3a3b142538a6e149703172fba200e3","tid":942031,"uid":67876,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"律師梁永鏗接受訪問時表示，市民在街上執到屬於他人擁有及具有價值的財物，例如現金等，沒有將財物交予警方反而擅自據為己有，其行為等同拾遺不報，有可能已觸犯盜竊罪，一旦罪名成立，最高刑期是判監10年。「因為呢啲財物根本就唔係屬於佢哋（執拾者）。財物擁有人如果表明唔要或者將財物丟去垃圾站，咁嘅情況去執就唔算有罪，未必觸犯到法律」。<br />\n好似佢話拍片從天而降<br />\n又無講明派街坊 都要俾翻警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T10:47:51.000Z","msg":"幣少記低銀紙號碼之後再去警署認頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f114af8b73591585d90da19dcd2e7ce2590d7dd","tid":942031,"uid":138834,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":